al and mark prices derived from its virtual AMM and decentralized limit order book. The vAMM ensures continuous liquidity while JIT (Just-In-Time) liquidity auctions optimize fills during volatile periods. Funding payments occur automatically through Drift's insurance fund mechanism, with rates typically ranging from -0.01% to 0.01% per hour for infrastructure tokens."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
